Well, I wanted to prefix these custom labels to provide info about their "origin". Currently these labels are not attached to k8s resources, but only instance metadata, however in case they would I think such namespace should be used (not necessarily this one).

In terms of name: "k8s.multicloud.onap.org" - I've derived it from project page (onap.org) and repository path (k8s.multicloud). I was also thinking about k8splugin.k8s.multicloud.onap.org or k8splugin.io (that is used in other place), but I don't really know if either of these is proper so I'm welcome for comments.

@Ritu - could you relate to this aspect?
